{"id":25450,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":8,"day":7}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"儿童园","column":"","genre":"","count":"73","ytitle":"","mtitle":"救难民","ftitle":"","authors":["林荣冈"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"林荣冈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难民苦，难民苦!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在夏天，尤其苦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋子小，人口多；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真苦得，要生病。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生了病，很可怜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请诸位，发慈心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捐药品，救难民；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真所谓，好良心。"}]}